data.description: Look no further...Welcome home to this cozy ranch located on over a half acre lot in well established Pebble Creek Subdivision in Jackson. With 3 spacious bedrooms ,2 full baths and a Possible 4th bedroom/bonus room this home has ample space for you and your family. Living room features vaulted ceilings and wood burning fireplace. Large private fenced back yard great for kids and pets, Or Jump in the above ground pool for summer fun! Don't wait this home won't last long!
